ygData.subject: All the Skill Analsys' (sic) Are Wrong
ygData.msgSnippet: ... All The Skill Analsys Are Wrong by KingOfFoolsTony This is just a minor error but many of the skills say (Levl +1) * 5 but thats wrong, its (level *5) + 5
ygData.messageBody:
I found this on the EQSong message board:

-----------------------------------------------

All The Skill Analsys' Are Wrong
by KingOfFoolsTony


This is just a minor error but many of the skills say (Levl +1) * 5 but
thats wrong, its (level *5) + 5

-----------------------------------------------

:-D

Windleaf wipes the tears from his eyes from laughing so hard.

I've just got to believe it was a joke, but I don't have faith that
people's algebra skills are all that great.

---Windleaf
